OL,3,CSewage overflows 'not good enough',
OL,4,Cboss of North West water supplier says
OL,6,FThe water firm behind historic sewage
OL,7,Fspills in Windermere has said issues
OL,8,Fcannot be fixed "instantly", as heavy
OL,9,Frainfall and storms in the North West
OL,10,Fof England have driven more flooding
OL,11,Fincidents.
OL,13,FThe chief executive of United
OL,14,FUtilities also said she was "alive to
OL,15,Fthe issues of trust and transparency"
OL,16,Fin the water sector after receiving a
OL,17,F#1.4 million pay packet last year.
