OL,3,CSewage overflows 'not good enough',
OL,4,Cboss of North West water supplier says
OL,6,F"It is heartbreaking... I am very
OL,7,Fclear about the need to improve in
OL,8,Fthis area," she told the committee.
OL,10,F"It is not something we're going to be
OL,11,Fable to fix instantly.
OL,13,F"It is a serious of infrastructure
OL,14,Fprogrammes... and at the same time,
OL,15,Fwe're going to have to look more long
OL,16,Fterm about how we react to the impacts
OL,17,Fof climate change, particularly in
OL,18,Fsome of the hot-spots in the North
OL,19,FWest."
