OL,3,CSewage overflows 'not good enough',
OL,4,Cboss of North West water supplier says
OL,6,FMs Beardmore added: "Our performance
OL,7,Fisn't good enough... we have one of
OL,8,Fthe highest rates of internal sewer
OL,9,Fflooding across the country."
OL,11,FThis is partly due to a higher level
OL,12,Fof rainfall in the region last year
OL,13,Fleading to more major storms and flash
OL,14,Fflooding, and a greater number of
OL,15,Fpower cuts.
OL,17,FShe said the company had "fast-
OL,18,Ftracked" a programme to rebuild all of
OL,19,Fthe wastewater treatment works around
OL,20,FLake Windermere and improve the water
OL,21,Fquality.
