OL,3,CSewage overflows 'not good enough',
OL,4,Cboss of North West water supplier says
OL,6,FUnited Utilities is set to increase
OL,7,Fconsumer bills by 32% over the coming
OL,8,Ffive years, which will help pay for a
OL,9,F#13.7 billion investment plan in the
OL,10,Fwider region between 2025 and 2030.
OL,12,FThe boss took home a pay packet of
OL,13,F#1.4 million last year, made up of a
OL,14,Fbase salary worth #690,000, plus
OL,15,Fbenefits, bonuses and long-term share
OL,16,Fawards.
