OL,6,FAsked by MPs to justify the bonuses,
OL,7,FMs Beardmore said: "Shareholders are
OL,8,Fentirely paying for that so it's not
OL,9,Fpassed onto customers int terms of
OL,10,Fcustomer bills."
OL,12,F"I think we're all very alive to the
OL,13,Fissue of remuneration and trust in the
OL,14,Fsector and the changes that need to
OL,15,Ffollow," she added.
